name: Volcano Eruptions
content:
Description: volcano eruptions during the last 10,000 years

[Source](https://volcano.si.edu/list_volcano_holocene.cfm)

Processing: several rows on the original .csv that had incomplete were deleted

Columns:

* Volcano Name (string): full name of the volcano
* Country (string): country where the volcano is located
* Type (string): type of the volcano 
* Last known eruption (string): date of the last known eruption
* Region (string): region where the volcano is located
* Latitude (numerical): latitude where the volcano is located
* Longitude(numerical): longitude where the volcano is located
* Elevation (numerical): elevation is meters of the volcano
* Dominant Rock Type (string): rock type of the volcano
* Tectonic Setting (string): tectonic setting of the volcano
